# Cloudflare Pages serves this file from the build output (dist/_headers) and
# applies these response headers to matching paths. Mirrors the three security
# headers the app's Caddyfile sets, scoped to the whole static landing. No CSP
# yet — the landing has no inline-script tuning to gate.
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: same-origin
